# Linux Log Analyzer

## Overview

This project analyzes Linux log files using Python to detect error messages and generate reports.

## Features

* Reads server log files
* Detects error messages
* Counts total errors
* Generates automated report

## Technologies Used

* Python
* Linux
* File Handling
* Git & GitHub

## How to Run

1. Navigate to project folder
2. Run:
   python3 log_analyzer.py

## Output

* Displays error messages
* Shows total error count
* Saves result in log_report.txt
